nodes.title: Note: About image size
widgets_values: You can use the latent from the **EmptySD3LatentImage** to replace **VAE Encode of image1 with latent**, so you can customize the image size.

nodes.title: Note: KSampler settings
widgets_values:
You can test and find the best setting by yourself. The following table is for reference.

| Model            | Steps | CFG |
|---------------------|---------------|---------------|
| Offical             | 50               | 4.0               
| fp8_e4m3fn             | 20                | 2.5               |
| fp8_e4m3fn + 4steps LoRA    | 4               | 1.0               |
| rapid AIO    | 4               | 1.0               |

**Not enable the lora** 

if you don't use the trigger

**Next Scene:**

in the prompt
enable if you want a DWpose from image3

**About my nodes**

The **McTextEncodeQwenImEditPlus** will scale your input to 1024Ã—1024 pixels. We use the size of your first input image. **My node use lancsoz resize instead of area resize of the Comfyui node.**
